{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "9081ad4b-d173-4933-b7db-46941af83352", "type": 201, "content": {"answer_steps": [], "preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/9081ad4b-d173-4933-b7db-46941af83352@1.pkg/1772597487888/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597488142", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/9081ad4b-d173-4933-b7db-46941af83352@1.pkg/1772597487888/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597488142"}, "identifier": "9081ad4b-d173-4933-b7db-46941af83352", "test_cases": "", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>本题考查中国应对机遇和挑战。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>面对当前的经济形势，我国应深刻认识错综复杂的国际环境带来的新挑战，增强风险意识，注重经济安全，立足基本国情保持战略定力，办好自己的事情。坚持合作共赢的理念，与世界共享发展机遇，促进共同繁荣。故D符合题意。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>A：应坚持多边主义，维护世界秩序，说法错误。&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>B：追求高质量发展，说法错误。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>C：风险危机只能尽量降低，不能杜绝，说法错误。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>4.2携手促发展</b></span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>（改编）当前正面临着世界百年未有之大变局，我国发展需要应对的风险和挑战、需要解决的矛盾和问题比以往更加错综复杂。为此我国需要（ &nbsp; &nbsp; ）</span></p></div>", "label": "", "title": "（改编）当前正面临着世界百年未有之大变局，我国发展需要应对的风险和挑战、需要解决的矛盾和问题比以往更加错综复杂。为此我国需要（     ）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {}, "time_dependent": false, "examples": {"responses": [], "feedbacks": [], "items": []}, "respons